A package is a physical folder structure that contains a group of classes & interfaces & sub-packages.

REALTIME EXAMPLES:
When you download a movie,song or games you make a different folder for each category.
_________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
ADVANTAGES :
1)Maintenance
2)Reusability
3)Access Control
4)Organized
____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
Types of Packages:
1)User-defined packages
2)Predefined packages
